reviewText: I've had mine for about 7 years. I still enjoy using it as much today as the day I set it up. I'm actually considering a second one in case mine breaks. I've gone through several high end treadmills and "pro" work out machines - none match this small and relatively inexpensive tool.

I've used the original AB-Doer for over 20 years...love the machine and the workout tapes... My advanced copy broke about 4 years ago...my order from Amazon was here before 4 days earlier than promised arrival date
In my 60's---six pack...need I say more?
